parameters: ストーリー　砦潜入
\n< Cecilia >This isn't where I wanted to come...!

\n< Cecilia >This is the main gate of the fortress! But, to get
out from this front yard, I need a key!

\n< Cecilia >Well, there's no fucking guard or anything! I
could just climb over the nearby wall... but...!

\n< Cecilia >This guy... won't let me escape, probably.
*panting* Damn, I've been caught up...

\n< Serena >Well... depending on how you look at it, the
situation has become simpler.

\n< Serena >In other words, all we need to do is defeat this
guy right here.

\n< Serena >Considering how difficult it was to escape from
the deepest part of that venue.

\n< Serena >I... don't really understand, but in a way, it
could be said that this monster turning everything
upside down was rather convenient.
\n< Cecilia >If we can win here, that is...

\n< Serena >Well... I have no idea who you are, what you want,
or what you're up to. It's all very confusing.
\n< Serena >I have to get out of here.
\n< Serena >I'm going to shake them off here.
\n< Serena >My name is Serena Fuoco L'Brillante de la Grazia.

\n< Serena >Oh god who rules over this world! I shall take
your life! I shall bestow upon you a shameful
death!
ストーリー　砦潜入　勝利
回想セーブ エンディング

\n< Serena >It took some effort due to my flexibility... but
once you have a physical form, there is a sound
that resides in your body. Waves. Rhythm.
\n< Serena >I've captured that sound and put on the Afaaville.

\n< Serena >The armor that envelops you is the armor of sound.
Resonating, vibrating, the bouncing sound becomes
a myriad of vibrations.
\n< Serena >And vibration is, in other words, heat.

\n< Serena >Splendore, as long as you are safe... that
alone... I...

\n< Cecilia >Don't mess with me, you bastard! Right now,
I'll...!

\n< Serena >It can't be helped... It's just their nature.
Splendore did nothing wrong.

\n< Serena >All evil resides within me. This child is merely
reacting to that ugliness.

\n< Serena >...Splendore. I apologize for making you feel
uncomfortable.

\n< Serena >Just a little longer, please keep sleeping... I'll
take you home soon...

\n< Serena >Ugh, it hurts... When I calm down, the pain
will...

\n< Serena >This... I might not be able to play the piano
anymore. I've given my parents more reasons to
scold me.

\n< Cecilia >Well then, Serena, for what purpose...? For what
purpose did you work so hard like this? This is
just...

\n< Serena >...I didn't do all this expecting anything in
return.

\n< Serena >I just wanted to repay the friendship. Even if
that time has already passed.

\n< Serena >I decided that, and I accomplished it just as
planned... That's why I am satisfied.

\n< Serena >Ah... Splendour...! Your white mane that I've even
dreamt about...!
\n< Serena >I won't let go anymore...! Never again...!

\n< Cecilia >...Sigh... I don't really understand what's going
on, but anyway, I guess this counts as a
successful operation... Is this okay?

\n< Cecilia >The fortress seems to be in complete disarray.
It's not like we have time to worry about it
anymore. Let's quietly retreat, shall we?
\n< Cecilia >By the way, what was that earlier?

\n< Serena >I once saw it in the sewer... A black slime. No...
Was it not a slime?

\n< Serena >Lady Catherine said that in the underground of
this town, there are numerous lingering thoughts
of stillborn children. Those thoughts gather
together and form a curse...

\n< Serena >That might have been the curse itself. I don't
know why it appeared here now, though...

\n< Serena >...Come to think of it, Lady Catherine told me to
show them some understanding...

\n< Cecilia >What is that woman saying? We're not exactly
close, you know.

\n< Cecilia >Serena doesn't have an obligation to deal with
such things. I gave her a good punch! Take that!

\n< Cecilia >Serena doesn't need to worry about that, so let's
not bring up such topics. Don't rain on our happy
ending.

\n< Serena >Yeah... I'm sorry, but I was already doing my best
just to help this child.

\n< Serena >Well, let's go home, Splendore. I'm sure Father
and Mother are very angry.
\n< Serena >Because I might cry if I get scolded.
ストーリー　砦潜入　敗北

\n< Serena >It seems like this monster is targeting me...!
Take Splendore and run...!
\n< Serena >Is this... the end...? In a place like this...
\n< Serena >It ended more quickly than I thought.
\n< Serena >Well, at least Splendore was saved.
\n< Serena >I couldn't hold that child in my arms again.
